A murder was reported on 2015-12-16 at about 16:00 at Kwamashu men&#8217;s hostel, Ntokozo Road, at Mazambane Shopping Centre. The deceased Indian male, has been identified as Imtiaz Ahmed Bux, 59 years old. It is alleged that Imtiaz closed his butchery and while he was walking to his vehicle he was approached by three armed african males who demanded cash from him, and when he refused, they then shot him in the chest. He managed to get inside his car and he died on the driver&#8217;s seat. Suspects failed to take the money and fled on foot. Two spent cartridges were found on the scene. Imtiaz was from Mhlathuzane in Chatsworth. Suspects are not known at this stage.